long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The easiest way to extract and copy CSS/Tailwind
CSS Finder is a new chrome SidePanel extension that help you design website more efficiently

-Effortlessly copy any CSS element with a single click. 
-D'ont search throught the dozens of HTML elements. Inspect in one click
-Every CSS element you extract is directly translated into its Tailwind equivalent
-Automatically embed the extracted CSS into a prebuilt HTML / REACT tag, ready for immediate use.

Try for free with limited access, pay if you like it !
